These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: whist, poker
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, romance
1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Game       | poker       | whist |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance       | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, plum
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, brown
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | plum     | kale |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Color   | brown  | ebony      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
House: palace, ranch-style
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the fan of country is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the palace house is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| House      | palace | ranch-style  |
| Color          | lavender    | blood-red   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

