.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, rock
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, climbing
1. the coach is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the fan of d&b is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Music-Genre           | d&b          | rock    |
| Sport     | climbing            | rugby       |

 